{"id":115702,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/10/奴隶贸易与失踪儿童/","date":"2010-10-23T15:30:43Z","modified":"2010-10-23T15:30:43Z","title":"奴隶贸易与失踪儿童","content":"<p><p><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> 奴隶贸易与失踪儿童</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">昨天收到最新一期的《读者文摘》，其中“</span><span>THE<br />\nNEW SLAVE TRADE</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”（新的奴隶贸易）一文，读的让人惊骇，也难以置信，文中列出了几个国家</span><span>/</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">地区的奴隶总数如下，美国</span><span>40,000</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，中东</span><span>61,000</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，欧盟</span><span>270,000</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，中国</span><span>300,000</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，拉丁美洲</span><span>/</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">加勒比地区</span><span>399,000</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，非洲</span><span>685,000</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，亚洲其它地区</span><span>4,100,000</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，印度</span><span>22,000,000</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。其中包括被出卖的、被贩卖的、被挟持的人口。</span><span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">今天在腾讯网上读到如下的图片新闻，同样让人震惊！</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“<b>家长寻找失踪孩子</b>”</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"><span>10</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>12</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日，河南郑州二七广场上，来自山西太原的冯建林在广场上展示两幅</span><span>50</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">米长的画卷，画卷上是</span><span>2000</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个失踪孩子的资料。冯建林因</span><span>9</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁女儿失踪而走上寻女路。如今，他和另外几名家长带着手中的</span><span>2000</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">名失踪孩子的资料，带着这些父母的期盼，开始全国巡回荀子的征程。</span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"><a href=\"http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/51db9792g9318e174e433\"><img src=\"http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/51db9792g9318e174e433&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<div>\n<p><a href=\"http://move.blog.sina.com.cn/admin/blogmove/blogmove_msn.php\">MSN空间完美搬家到新浪博客!</a></p>\n</div>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}